    <item>
      <title>未来真正的下行风险：Chris Watling</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-21/real-downside-risk-ahead-chris-watling-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Longview Economics 首席执行官兼首席市场策略师 Chris Watling 表示，未来确实存在一些下行风险，未来两周对于观察价格走势至关重要。他进一步补充说，债券和股票之间的相关性不断从 60-40 的平衡中发生变化。他在彭博简报上与 Dani Burger 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-21/real-downside-risk-ahead-chris-watling-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:25:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BP 经济学家称 OPEC+ 恢复石油产量的空间有限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/bp-economist-says-opec-has-limited-scope-to-restore-oil-output</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司首席经济学家斯宾塞·戴尔表示，鉴于美国、巴西和圭亚那的供应增加，OPEC+ 增产的空间有限，因为这将给油价带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/bp-economist-says-opec-has-limited-scope-to-restore-oil-output</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:13:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称，比特币矿商 Bitfarms 正在洽谈以 1.64 亿美元收购 Stronghold</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/bitcoin-miner-bitfarms-in-talks-to-acquire-stronghold-in-all-stock-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，比特币挖矿公司 Bitfarms Ltd. 正就以约 1.64 亿美元收购 Stronghold Digital Mining Inc. 进行谈判，同时抵御 Riot Platforms Inc. 的收购企图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/bitcoin-miner-bitfarms-in-talks-to-acquire-stronghold-in-all-stock-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员期待美国就业数据支撑美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/traders-look-to-us-jobs-data-to-support-the-rally-in-treasuries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[那些希望美国国债进一步上涨的投资者将关注美国劳动力市场的修订数据，以寻找美联储需要开始大幅降息的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/traders-look-to-us-jobs-data-to-support-the-rally-in-treasuries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔面临政策十字路口，所有人的目光都集中在杰克逊霍尔会议上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/powell-confronts-policy-crossroads-with-all-eyes-on-jackson-hole</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔将于周五开启美联储通胀之战的下一章，预计他将为降息做好准备，同时向投资者保证政策制定者能够避免经济急剧放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/powell-confronts-policy-crossroads-with-all-eyes-on-jackson-hole</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债务协议进入选举日程，斯里兰卡债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/sri-lanka-bonds-decline-as-debt-deal-runs-into-election-calendar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者担心下个月的总统大选可能会推迟与债权人完成债务重组协议的时间，斯里兰卡的美元债券价格正在走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/sri-lanka-bonds-decline-as-debt-deal-runs-into-election-calendar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:56:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐科威盟友试图削弱法院裁决，引发强烈抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/court-ruling-deals-blow-to-jokowi-s-dynastic-legacy-in-indonesia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼的紧张局势正在加剧，周三，印尼一些议员采取行动推翻了一项法院判决，该判决原本将阻止印尼总统佐科·维多多的小儿子参加今年的一场关键选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/court-ruling-deals-blow-to-jokowi-s-dynastic-legacy-in-indonesia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 06:35:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
